About Me

Hey, am Dennis! Welcome to my digital garden where I share my thoughts and experience aspects I find endlessly facsinating like coding, design & life.

I have worked as a professional software engineer consultant for various clients worldwide and this has helped me with insights on what it takes to run a successful project. My commitment for attention to details and passion for processes have amassed me with a wealth of experience for working in agile environments.

My main interest is in the design of open source software systems and in being frugal both as an independent contributor and for the good of development teams in delivering value.

I always love and appreciate meeting new people and am looking forward to connecting with a few. Feel free to contact me and say hi

Twitter

What am currently doing

Updated April, 2023
Nothing much going on. I spend most of my time writing software for paid clients and my start up as am currently building software products that am hoping to launch soon! Generating absolutely high quality and first-class output truly means the world to me.

My company is about to unveil an incredible CRM platform that will transform the way you manage your business relationships. Be the first to experience the power of our CRM platform by joining my exclusive waiting list. By signing up, you'll gain early access, receive exciting updates, and unlock special perks! Don't miss out on this opportunity to supercharge your business. Visit{" "} Sign Up Page {" "} now to join the waiting list! Together, let's take your business to new heights!

I recently started early evening and sometimes even morning workouts, and eating vegetables and fruits. It's been nice this far and I intend to improve and uphold the discipline going forward.

Feeling overwhelmed. . . !?

  1. You come across so many learning resources including blogs, papers, courses and tutorials etc and they makes it even more difficult to know where to start as others are either too basic or too advanced?

  2. Feeling confused and deciding on which resource is worth the time and effort is a challenge and you feel overwhelmed?

  3. Again, there are a lot of annoying noise on the internet these days. Have you tried seeking answers to your questions online then you experience pop ups and cluterring from ads, affiliates and sponsored content all over while navigating?

If this is true for you, don't worry. I feel your pain and I've got you covered since I have been through the same as well.

I want to help you, yes! And{" "} the first step is to subscribe to my newsletter so that you get notified straight to your inbox, and stay up-to-date

I strongly support and believe in the deep exchange of knowledge free from noise, fluff and junk. And, I welcome you to be part of my monthly newsletter on this young and ever evolving technology space, on business and on life!
